Note on the project name
-------------------------
"Crenel" is a WORKING NAME and is not yet final. The name appears in this NOTICE,
in the LICENSE appendix boilerplate, in the Go module path (go.mod), and in
internal/config/naming.go, which centralizes every other user-visible occurrence.
A rename touches those points and is intended to be a single find/replace; the
NOTICE attribution above should be updated to the final project name at that time.

